# --- OpenAI (server-side only) -------------------------------------------------
# Used exclusively by the Vercel serverless function in /api. Do NOT prefix with
# VITE_ — that would inline the secret into the browser bundle. Set the real
# value locally in .env (git-ignored) and in Vercel → Settings → Environment
# Variables for Production + Preview.
OPENAI_API_KEY=
# Optional. Defaults to gpt-4o-mini (fast + cheap).
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
